      "role": "user",
      "content": "i honestly dont even know what to do anymore. everything i worked for these last 4 years... the lab results, the funding, the dissertation... it just feels like it's all gone. i feel like i've wasted my entire life on a version of myself that doesn't even exist anymore. i'm just so tired. like, deep in my bones, exhausted. i don't see the point in waking up tomorrow just to fail again.",
